data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F19%2F201046_51657c6fa04c6cd3c251856b0ae3630e.jpg&h=7f97980b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n豐臣氏！<br />\n豐臣秀吉嘅事蹟真係好神奇，由平民變成天下人</blockquote><br />\n豐臣氏好似絕左後?</blockquote><br />\n好旁系好似有，都係冇能力利用太閣的威信做號召的人。<br />\n<br />\n直系就死光，秀長的後代都係早死，關白秀次一家被處死。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n豐臣氏既代表，要由返木下家定一系既後代出席<br />\n而木下家定係北政所（淺野寧寧）既兄長，靠妹妹而改姓木下，所以話⋯豐臣一族後代都要靠老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b11e831499cd744d4b8d029069729b754739e8","tid":364974,"uid":37942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T14:20:59.000Z","msg":"日本文化真係好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本刀都好撚型棍"},{"pid":"ade1d4bcde6b371af2725002939e52286979d2e5","tid":364974,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T14:24:19.000Z","msg":"附註：現任木下家督係木下崇俊（第19代），江戶時代為北九州豐後日出藩藩主，而家從事地產業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c781916ac54fbe634fc7f360c208c3fb4d3f7b8b","tid":364974,"uid":82097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T14:29:40.000Z","msg":"想知有無用動物做主題既家紋<br />\n例如狼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea770a52cb58593d67babbcdf432e5ea844476ea","tid":364974,"uid":23026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T14:48:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/19/224719_a10c3d210c9183f1a200d2f59daace4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F19%2F224719_a10c3d210c9183f1a200d2f59daace4e.jpg&h=62708e10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢本算正野，都算幾齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b778be4f3e1178acdcbbf2b466bd8fb790d5a0b0","tid":364974,"uid":117458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T15:42:05.00